gh 6:00 PM on May 1, 2020. A very special thank you to our faculty, medical professionals, environmental services staff, and others who are working tirelessly on the front lines!  The new training deadline is May 1, 2020 at 6:00 PM CT.  See more: University Ethics and Compliance Office Announcement      Modified on March 23, 2020                 UIC Logo        Office for Access and Equity         Helpful Links    Office of Diversity    Disability Resource Center    Human Resources    Dean of Students    Campus Advocacy Network    UIC Police         Contact   809 S. Marshfield Ave., Room 717, Chicago, IL 60612-7207  Phone: (312) 996-8670  oae@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  Â© 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 